  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "This measure would affirm the Legislature's commitment to Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion (DEI) and encourage local, state, and federal policymakers, among other organizations, to adopt and uphold DEI principles."
    }
